    "v0.3.0": {
      "created_at": "2026-06-02T08:17:40Z",
      "description": "This update adds automatically sending the admin commands to the server.\r\nA few useful commands:\r\n - /set_password: \r\n     - sets the admin password for the current connection (nothing to delete the password)\r\n     - will overwrite previous passwords of seeds with the exact same player list\r\n     - password is automatically encrypted, only decrypted when used to send the room changes (the encryption key is unique per device)\r\n- /load_keys: loads all (encrypted) passwords\r\n- /save: save the current (encrypted) passwords (and deletion thereof)\r\n- /tray: move the window to a tray icon so you can have it running in the background without bothering you (only available on os with tray icons)",
